  "title": "Federation Activity",
  "story": [
    {
      "text": "Where is all the activity in the Federation? How can I view an individuals activity across sites that they own, or view the activity of a group of individuals?",
      "id": "065f5f141c503282",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "text": "- [[Filtered Federation Activity]]\n- [[Recent Federation Activity]]\n- [[Changes to this Site]]\n- [[Research Group Activity]]\n- [[Recent Changes]]\n",
      "id": "29c298a863170d80",
      "type": "markdown"
    },
    {
      "text": "# Tools\n",
      "id": "550014712c7fad41",
      "type": "markdown"
    },
    {
      "text": "In [[the federation]] we not only involve ourselves in [[writing with strangers]], but we [[Create tools and code]]:\n",
      "id": "a0336dc7ec30edbb",
      "type": "markdown"
    },
    {
      "text": "- [[Fedwiki Tools]]\n- [[Recycled Pages]]\n- [[Local Changes]]\n",
      "id": "4e2fab4f4ec2db54",
      "type": "markdown"
    },
    {
      "text": "[[Drop]] any web page on the transporter below to bring content into the [[federation]] with appropriate [[accreditation]].",
      "id": "2337e593fa7a7966",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "text": "POST https://rest.livecode.world/imagine",
      "id": "10ea2af363e51a5f",
      "type": "transport"
    },
    {
      "text": "[[Search]] for what you need with our [[Little Green Box]]:",
      "id": "58e5f8fc5f38e0fc",
      "type": "markdown"
    },
    {
      "type": "html",
      "id": "b4635d46ac35eb1b",
      "text": "<div align=right style=\"background-color:lightgreen;color:black;padding:12px;\">\n\n<form data-lpignore=\"true\" action=\"https://rest.livecode.world/search/cse\">\n\nEnter [[federation search query]]\n\n<br>\n  <input name=search_Term value='wiki' \n size=58>\n  <input name=cse_Name value='cse_Name' type=hidden>\n  <input type=\"submit\">\n</form>\n</div>"
    },
    {
      "text": "# Recent Changes\n",
      "id": "e8dc02f24c3cdf40",
      "type": "markdown"
    },
    {
      "text": "View [[neighborhood]] activity in the __last 4 weeks__ below:",
      "id": "aa3bd7b0e3e69d36",
      "type": "markdown"
    },
    {
      "text": "SINCE 4 weeks",
      "id": "e9e9f102158e1382",
      "type": "activity"
    },
    {
      "text": "# Rosters\n",
      "id": "7d75b628aa86a6c9",
      "type": "markdown"
    },
    {
      "text": "The following [[active roster]] is generated by fetching Ward's [[Weekly Roster]] and stripping out the individual day/time categories and adding \"Recent Federation Activity]] as a roster category so it can be used by an activity view.\n",
      "id": "ae2f71253d96f109",
      "type": "markdown"
    },
    {
      "text": "ROSTER rest.livecode.world/recent",
      "id": "f07b85379c93cbbb",
      "type": "roster"
    },
    {
      "text": "The following [[active roster]] is generated by fetching Ward's [[Weekly Roster]] and removing any domains it finds that are on the [[Atopia Server]]. It is used by the [[Filtered Recent Activity]] wiki-page.\n",
      "id": "7dcecb2eec4aebda",
      "type": "markdown"
    },
    {
      "id": "1f91e852406d52a0",
      "type": "roster",
      "text": "ROSTER rest.livecode.world/filtered",
      "alias": "f07b85379c93cbbb"
    },
